Package: cacheR
Type: Package
Title: Recursive File-Based Caching With Call Tree Introspection
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Vedran", "Franke",
           email = "vedran.franke@mdc-berlin.de",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Tools for caching function results to disk while tracking
    recursive parent-child relationships between cached calls.
    Provides utilities to inspect the cache tree for debugging
    and provenance.
